    {
      "id": "optimistic_8_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_8",
      "description": "Clean, honest car in good overall condition and a big step up from a fixer-upper. It presents well, drives nicely, and should make a solid, enjoyable driver for its next owner, with only typical signs of age and use. A great option for someone who wants a well-kept car at a sensible price.",
