    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "Well-kept, good-condition example that presents nicely overall and should make a satisfying driver or local show car. The paint, body, and interior all show well, with the kind of light cosmetic wear and age-related imperfections you\u2019d expect from an honest used classic rather than a fully restored or mint car. It appears to have been maintained and enjoyed, and a buyer should expect a solid, attractive car that is usable as-is while still leaving room for cosmetic or detail-oriented improvement depending on your standards.",
      "price": 34900.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
